						<div class="postbody">Famitracker....instrument...arpeggio...type | 0 4 7 (must have a pipe first), or | 0 4 7 4<br /><br />Also, other intervals are interesting...<br />0 4 11 4<br />0 4 12 4<br />0 5 12 5<br />0 2 7 2<br />0 7 14 7<br />etc...<br /><br />EDIT - 'pipe' is slang for a vertical bar.</div>

					
